
                                   nfsd 
                                  ------

1. Introduction
----------------

The nfsd template provides a mechanism to build a NSFD kernel module for
NFS server capability on the target.


2. Usage
--------

Add this template using the following configure script option.
ie.: --templates feature/nfsd

This will ensure the required kernel config values are set. 


3. Installation
----------------

This template will include the nfsd kernel module in the root filesystem.
No additional installation steps are required. You will find the
kernel modules installed in /lib/modules/<kernel-version>/kernel/fs/nfsd
in the root filesystem.
